    <item>
      <title>罢工期限临近，安大略省酒类商店准备停业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/ontario-liquor-stores-prepare-for-shutdown-as-strike-deadline-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安大略省国有酒类零售商正准备最早于周五举行罢工，同时继续进行劳资谈判，以避免关闭加拿大人口最多的省份的 669 家商店。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/ontario-liquor-stores-prepare-for-shutdown-as-strike-deadline-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 14:23:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉的旧策略未能赢得巴西敌对农民的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/lula-s-old-playbook-fails-to-win-over-hostile-brazilian-farmers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦周三公布的创纪录农作物融资计划遵循了曾经使他成为世界上最受欢迎的总统之一的策略：通过向重要行业提供政府援助，他既可以提振巴西经济，又可以将怀疑者转变为支持者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/lula-s-old-playbook-fails-to-win-over-hostile-brazilian-farmers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 13:34:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
